 Katha (film)|Burrakatha]]''\n| Bongaram Hema \n|\n|-\n|''[[Software Sudheer]]''\n| Doctor\n|\n|-\n|''[[Iddari Lokam Okate]]''\n| Mukesh\n|\n|}\n\n==Notes==\n{{notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb name|3760044}}\n* [http://chithr.com/video/play/1427/banerjee-interviews-prithviraj-%2830-years-industry-fame%29-part-2.html Chithr.com]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Prudhviraj}}\n[[Category:Telugu comedians]]\n[[Category:Telugu male actors]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1964 births]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2015}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=December 2015}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Pruthviraj\n| image              = \n| caption            = \n| birth_name         = Balireddy Pruthviraj\n| birth_place        = [[Tadepalligudem]], [[West Godavari district]], [[Andhra Pradesh]], [[India]]\n| death_date         = \n| death_place        = \n| residence          = [[Hyderabad]], [[Telangana]], [[India]],\n[[Tirupati|Tirupathi]], [[Andhra Pradesh]], [[India]]\n| father             = Balireddy Subbarao\n| occupation         = Actor, Politician, Ex-SVBC channel chairman\n| education          = M.A\n| birth_date         = {{Birth date and age|1964|8|6}}\n| alma_mater         = [[Andhra University]], [[Visakhapatnam]]\n| Political party    = [[YSR Congress Party]]\n}}\n\n'''Balireddy Prudhviraj''' (born August 6, 1964) is a comedian in [[Telugu cinema|Telugu]].<ref name=\"Times of India News1\">{{cite web|last1=Hemanth|first1=Kumar|title=Prudhvi Raj gets rave reviews for his role in Loukyam|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Prudhvi-Raj-gets-rave-reviews-for-his-role-in-Loukyam/articleshow/43525908.cms|website=timesofindia.indiatimes.com|publisher=Times of India|accessdate=12 December 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"deccanchronicle\">{{cite web|last1=Kavirayani|first1=Suresh|title=It\u2019s not been an easy journey: Prudhviraj|url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/150805/entertainment-tollywood/article/it%E2%80%99s-not-been-easy-journey-prudhviraj|website=deccanchronicle.com|publisher=Deccan Chronicle|accessdate=13 December 2016}}</ref> He was introduced by [[Prabhakar Reddy]].<ref name=\"Telugu 360 interview\">{{cite web|last1=Yalavarthi|first1=Sunita|title=Exclusive Interview with Prudhviraj (30 years industry)|url=https://www.telugu360.com/exclusive-interview-with-prudhviraj-comedian/|website=telugu360.com|publisher=Telugu 360|accessdate=12 December 2016}}</ref> Later he acted in ''[[Aa Okkati Adakku]]''. During this movie Prudhviraj spent 40 days with [[Rao Gopala Rao]] where he learned about the industry. He acted in more than 100 movies. He is noted for his role of \"30 Years Industry\", in [[Krishna Vamsi|Krishna Vamsi's]] movie, ''[[Khadgam]]''.<ref name=\"thehindu.com\">{{cite web|last1=Y.|first1=Sunita Chowdhary|title=Patience pays, finally for Prudhviraj|url=http://www.thehindu.com/features/metroplus/the-actor-is-in-demand-for-a-lot-of-comic-roles/article8029001.ece|website=thehindu.com|publisher=[[The Hindu]]|accessdate=14 December 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.teluguportals.com/2012/03/tori-live-show-with-4/#.UEOnlGYpLzo |title=TORI Live Show with Comedian Prithviraj |publisher=teluguportals.com |date=2012-03-14 |accessdate=2012-10-01}}</ref> He worked as chairman of [[SVBC TV|SVBC]] channel which was run by [[Tirumala Tirupati Devasthanams]] until January 12, 2020.\n\nOn January 11, 2020, an obscene illicit conversation between Prudhviraj and his female employee working in SVBC was found out and broadcast by the channel [[99TV]]. Subsequently he was found guilty and was asked to resign from his SVBC chairman post.<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m6VdbkNRjOo</ref>\n\n==Biography==\nPrudhviraj (born Balireddy Prudhviraj), is a famous comedian in [[Telugu film industry]]. He was born August 6 at [[Tadepalligudem]], West Godavari District, Andhra Pradesh. He was introduced by famous Dr. Prabakar Reddy and [[E V V Satyanarayana]] in their first film ''[[Aa Okkati Adakku]]''. During this film he spent forty days with [[Rao Gopala Rao]], where he learnt about the film industry. He played many roles in about 100 films. He was well recognized for his dialogue \u201c30 Years Industry ikkada\u201d in [[Krishna Vamsi]]'s film ''[[Khadgam]]'' and this film changed his fate.\n\nPrudhviraj hails from a respected farmer family in Tadepalligudem. Prudhviraj completed his master's degree in Economics from Andhra University. Since childhood, he participated in many stage shows and cultural activities. From his childhood, he had a dream to work in movies. With that interest, he entered into the industry. Prudhvi Raj's mother also supported him a lot to enter into the industry. After his debut film \u201cAa Okkati Adakku\u201d he left Chennai. Then Prudhviraj tried his luck in [[Tamil film industry]] but unfortunately he failed there.\n\nAgain he returned to the Telugu film industry and tested his luck. With the movie Kadgam, Prudhviraj became very popular. Before acting in Kadgam he worked in a hotel as a receptionist and also in a guest house.\n\nPrudhviraj is mostly suitable for comedy roles. His dialogue delivery and comedy in films is very effective. He had a well-noted role in the movie Loukyam.\n\nPrudhviraj played roles with top Tollywood actors such as [[Ravi Teja]], [[Daggubati Venkatesh|Venkatesh]], [[Ram Charan]], [[Pawan Kalyan]], [[Mahesh Babu]], [[Rajendra Prasad (actor)|Rajendra Prasad's]], [[Allu Arjun]], [[Gopichand (actor)|Gopichand]] and [[Nithiin]].\n\nHe has been nominated as chairman of [[SVBC TV|Sri Venkateswara Bhakti Channel]] in 2019. On 11 January 2020, his Audio tape recording with female employee of SVBC channel went viral in Youtube and SVBC employees protested urging him to resign from his post of chairman of Svbc channel.\n\nOn 11 January 2020, Prudhviraj resigned as chairman of [[SVBC TV|Sri Venkateswara Bhakti Channel]].\n\n==Filmography==\n{| class=\"wikitable